title: Flexi Cable Wrap to Organize Cords Behind Computer & TV by UT Wire
description:
UT Wire - Flexible Cable Wrap 

Expandable Flexi Cable Wrap that wraps around bundles of cables or cords to keep them organized. Made from a soft and flexible material, Flexi Cable Wrap leaves no plastic cuts from sharp edges on your fingers when inserting cords. No complicated tools are needed for installation. It's a smart expandable system that easily self wraps and conforms to bundle cords. 

"Simple Design, Big Solution"

For more information, please visit www.ut-wire.com/fcw
